Sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: cells were treated with 1 µM JQ1 for 24h
Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: Cells were grown in RPMI supplemented with 20% fetal bovine serum, 1% glutamin and 1% penicilin/streptomycin
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was extracted using the miRNAeasy mini kit (Qiagen). TruSeq Stranded Total RNA sample prep kit (Illumina) was used for the preparation of sequencing libraries., RNA libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard Illumina protocols
Sample_data_processing: fastq files were aligned to GRCh38 primary annotation with STARv2.4.2a using a 2-pass strategy. In the first pass gencode.v25 was used as guide, in the second pass all sjdb files from the first pass were used as guide, Genes were quantified by STARv2.4.2a on Gencode.v25
Supplementary_files_format_and_content: reads per gene as generated by STAR2.4.2a
